title: Verify that created predefined apps key-value pairs are displayed correctly
custom_steps:
Enable generic_header_insertion feature

Go to tenant web ui
Go to settings->Manage->Header Insertion
click on "Add New Key-Value Pair"
click on "Select application" dropdown menu
Create the predefined app Egnyte
Create the predefined app Dropbox
Ensure app, key and value details are displayed as per configuration
custom_expected: WebUI Page should shown configured app, key and value details
